  "3037410": {
    "name": "Fish Idle 2: Underwater Mystery",
    "steam_appid": 3037410,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "跳入你的雨靴，跳上你的船！我们要去钓鱼了，在Fish Idle 2: Underwater Mystery中，这是一款独特的闲置钓鱼街机游戏，具有流畅的图形和直观的机制。我们没有时间挥动钓鱼竿，所以让我们简化流程！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >简单轻松的钓鱼</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e2114c143866e818f6d42ef80b8d8bd9.poster.avif?t=1740479788\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e2114c143866e818f6d42ef80b8d8bd9.webm?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e2114c143866e818f6d42ef80b8d8bd9.mp4?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>让我们从基础开始。一切都是自动化的：鱼一靠近你就开始咬钩，资源指标会在你专注于有效管理你的鱼类王国时通知你。游戏提供了有利的升级，以增强你的闲置钓鱼能力，帮助你成为真正的鱼类大亨。你仍然需要驾驶你的船追逐鱼群并避开障碍物，所以不要被你的经济成就分心！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >升级你的鱼类王国</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e5cb8c4e92c8fb34195fb1045b82c4c5.poster.avif?t=1740479788\" width=598 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e5cb8c4e92c8fb34195fb1045b82c4c5.webm?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/e5cb8c4e92c8fb34195fb1045b82c4c5.mp4?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>一旦你的船舱满了，是时候升级了！提高钓鱼速度的升级让你能够捕获更多更稀有的鱼种，而增加的储存容量让你能够在船上装载更多的鱼。提升你的船速和防御能力，以防撞击，并改进你的钓鱼竿，一次投放多根鱼线。这一切都是为了以最有效的方式最大化你的收益，所以你需要动脑筋找出通往成功的最佳方法！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >做大做强</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/110c901d3f38aebbc3bc281e2909c29f.poster.avif?t=1740479788\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/110c901d3f38aebbc3bc281e2909c29f.webm?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/110c901d3f38aebbc3bc281e2909c29f.mp4?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>就像现实生活中一样，成为鱼类大亨需要通过多种方式从你的捕获物中获利。闲置鱼场允许你投资并获得被动收入，而黑市则让你可以将你的鱼类王国提升到超出OSHA标准的水平。机器人商店允许你雇佣猎鱼船、渔船和货船为你钓鱼并运送捕获物，从而增加你的收入。如果你喜欢日内交易，有一个货币交易所提供一些特别的好处。逃税不是犯罪，如果你想做大做强，这是你的义务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >现在去钓鱼</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/0a07bc7fe70b65226af4828009d5a90f.poster.avif?t=1740479788\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/0a07bc7fe70b65226af4828009d5a90f.webm?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3037410/extras/0a07bc7fe70b65226af4828009d5a90f.mp4?t=1740479788\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>准备好潜入鱼类王国，在Fish Idle 2: Underwater Mystery中成为终极鱼类大亨！</strong>",
